  "title": "Service Crew/ Supervisor (Spanish cuisine) - 2323",
  "description": "<p><strong>Service Crew/ Supervisor (Spanish cuisine) </strong></p>\n<p>5.5 days, or 5 days (if not busy), 44 hours per week</p>\n<p>Salary: $2800-$3000 + OT</p>\n<p>Location: Guoco Tower, Tanjong Pagar</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job scope:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Greet customers warmly, take orders, serve food and beverages, and ensure a positive dining experience.</li>\n  <li>Accurately communicate orders to the kitchen and ensure correct delivery to tables.</li>\n  <li>Have a thorough understanding of the menu, including specials and ingredients, to answer questions and make recommendations.</li>\n  <li>Handle cash and credit card transactions accurately</li>\n  <li>Clearing dirty dishes, cleaning and resetting tables for the next customers, and ensuring the dining area remains tidy and organized</li>\n  <li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>With at least 1-2 years of relevant experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>To expedite the process interested candidates may contact me with your resume via:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Whatsapp: +65 8012 4526(Alvin)</p>\n<p>Alvin Chua Ming Jing | R23116192</p>\n<p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | 14C7279</p>\n<p><br></p>",
